article_id:2549,category_name:News,title_name:A Wind Focus Summon Showcase Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>A Wind Focus summon showcase started on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1634536800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>In the Wind Focus summon showcase, only wind-attuned adventurers and dragons will appear.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Note: The roster for this summon showcase does not include adventurers and dragons that are attuned to elements other than wind.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for featured summons:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1634536800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1635487199"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the 5★ adventurers and a 5★ dragon eligible to appear in the Wind Focus summon showcase below.</div><div><br></div><div>5★ adventurers:</div><div>
